Titolo: River City: Tokyo Rumble

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: River City: Tokyo Rumble is a beat'em up in the River City series published by Natsume in the west. It is most similar to River City Ransom with RPG-like mechanics and doing jobs to learn new moves. It also features a 4 player arena and dodgeball modes that use download play. Unlike other games in the Kunio-kun series, Tokyo Rumble did not alter its characters and setting upon localization.

Genere: Beat \'em up

Valutazione: N/A
